    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in mint, showroom condition and has been meticulously preserved by its previous owner. The exterior paint retains its original deep luster with absolutely no scratches, dents, or chips, while the interior remains in flawless state, still possessing that new-car feel. Every mechanical and electronic component functions perfectly, making this an ideal find for a collector or a buyer seeking a vehicle that is indistinguishable from new. This is a rare opportunity to own a perfectly maintained example of this model.",
