    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint, showroom condition, appearing exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. The exterior paint is flawless, with a deep, mirror-like finish and no chips, scratches, or imperfections of any kind. Inside, the cabin remains in factory-fresh state, with the leather upholstery still smelling new and all electronic components functioning perfectly. This is a rare opportunity to own a meticulously preserved example that has been kept in a climate-controlled environment and never driven in inclement weather.",
      "price": 49500.0,
